The &lt;a href="America%20Cup%20of%20Volleyball"&gt;2000 Volleyball America's Cup&lt;/a&gt; was the third edition of the annual &lt;a href="volleyball"&gt;Men's Volleyball Tournament&lt;/a&gt;, played by six countries from North-, Central- and South America. The tournament was held from August 11 to August 20, 2000 in &lt;a href="S%C3%A3o%20Bernardo%20do%20Campo"&gt;São Bernardo&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Brazil"&gt;Brazil&lt;/a&gt;.
